# Next.js Agentic Rules (@akr/web)

## Architecture
- Use App Router (src/app).
- Prefer Server Components for data fetching.
- Use Client Components only when necessary for interactivity.

## Styling
- Tailwind CSS 4+ (using @tailwindcss/postcss).
- Maintain a premium design system:
  - Custom colors in `tailwind.config.ts`.
  - Glassmorphism effects.
  - Smooth transitions using Framer Motion (if added later).

## Performance
- Optimize images using `next/image`.
- Implement proper loading states with `loading.tsx`.
- Use `error.tsx` for graceful error handling.

## Code Quality
- Strict TypeScript.
- Descriptive component names.
- Modularize components into `src/components`.
